snippet.title: Best VGM 2275 - Dark Souls III - Abyss Watchers
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS4 / XB1 / PC
Dark Souls III (2016)
Abyss Watchers
Yuka Kitamura

Artwork: http://img1.joyreactor.cc/pics/post/full/Dark-Souls-3-Dark-Souls-%D1%84%D1%8D%D0%BD%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%BC%D1%8B-Abyss-Watcher-3002323.jpeg
